                                   Install                                      
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

• Build Maya

  bzr branch lp:maya
  cd maya
  mkdir build; cd build
  cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
  make
  sudo make install
  
  Alternatively, you could run
  
  ./install.sh
  
  in the project root to install Maya.

• Bugs

  If you find bugs in this installation guide or in Maya itself, please report them at
  https://launchpad.net/maya/+filebug


